{
  "stem": "26585.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know how these trains-- the Orient Express, you go out of the compartment and long hallway, beautiful windows.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You look out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so my sister and I went there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jean Manzalia ?] came and stood with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother said, Maxl, you don't have to say no right away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just play along.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The guy can help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tell you, she was terrific.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were complimenting each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father is so straightforward, and my mother always looking-- wonderful, just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He told us he was going to Sofia and from there back to Germany and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he wants to see us in Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We arrived in Zagreb at midnight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the strange language, you couldn't even make out words.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All you heard were sounds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we were told you'll get along with French, and never utter a German word.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Monsieur [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Manzalia ?] got out of the train and said something to the conductor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said, you are strangers here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just changed my mind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm going to stay with you and see that you're settled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My father said, we are to go across from the station is a hotel where our friend told us to go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, I will go quickly through this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He stayed with us two days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Easter Sunday he showed us Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Beautiful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, the food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he showed us the outdoor cafes and the restaurants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I think we got probably sick eating all that food that we hadn't had in a long time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then he left, but took our address where we were at that time, so that we were to leave-- every time we left, we were to-- and we did.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
